{"tid":2403432,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話英國唔好，幾時整份文件講 《人間地獄——英國》？？","createTime":"2021-02-11T05:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T05:45:36.000Z","uid":207634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c7ef45fa17e17643c98bbf245f8f98228fa744","tid":2403432,"uid":207634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:45:36.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨對<del>香港</del><strong><span class=\"red\">英國</span></strong>進行醜化宣傳，發表一份文件，叫《人間地獄&mdash;&mdash;<del>香港</del><strong><span class=\"red\">英國</span></strong>》，其中將會是如此描述：<br />\n<br />\n<del>香港</del><strong><span class=\"red\">英國</span></strong>是世界上最荒淫的城市；<br />\n<del>香港</del><strong><span class=\"red\">英國</span></strong>黑社會橫行；<br />\n<del>香港</del><strong><span class=\"red\">英國</span></strong>是最大的製毒販毒基地；<br />\n<del>香港</del><strong><span class=\"red\">英國</span></strong>自殺者是世界上有數的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%80%83%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=5a75b8d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%80%83%E6%B8%AF</a>"}]}